## v16.3 - Verify that files obtained from untrusted sources are validated to be of expected type and scanned by antivirus scanners to prevent upload of known malicious content.

### Why is this required?

Many attacks can occur by masquerading a malicious file as a legitimate file such as a .jpg or .wmv file.

### Applicability (Level 1)

This objective applies to all apps.

### Guidelines for developers

Maintain regular updates of anti-virus software.  This process should be automated when possible.
